    INSERT INTO artwork (slug, artwork_name, artist_slug, price, size_in, size_cm, description, additional_information, material, medium, image)    VALUES ('valentine-henriette-prax-le-paysan-au-bord-de-la-mer', 'le paysan au bord de la mer', 'valentine-henriette-prax', '14000000', '19 7/10 × 23 3/5 in', '50 × 60 cm', 'None', '<p>Prax was one of relatively few women artists to get established in the post-war years, leading a tumultuous life entwined in the Parisian artworld married to Ossip Zadkine. She became renowned for her surreal fantastical scenes, such as this excellent example, which she exhibited widely, including at the Venice Biennale as early as 1928, and culminating in a retrospective at the Musée d’Art Moderne in 1976. She now has significant museum representation and the Musée Zadkine held an exhibition highlighting her life in 2023.</p>', '''Includes gouache; fresco; ink and wash; oil painting; screen painting; scroll painting; tempera; watercolor.''', '''Oil on canvas''', 'https://d7hftxdivxxvm.cloudfront.net?height=746&quality=80&resize_to=fit&src=https%3A%2F%2Fd32dm0rphc51dk.cloudfront.net%2F2H7iChbolcszD8TzE_zcHA%2Fnormalized.jpg&width=800')    
    INSERT INTO artwork (slug, artwork_name, artist_slug, price, size_in, size_cm, description, additional_information, material, medium, image)    VALUES ('federico-pinto-schmid-mrs-wood', 'mrs wood', 'federico-pinto-schmid', '610000', '48 × 76 in', '121.9 × 193 cm', 'None', '<p>Designs, shapes, and colors find a balance between a polite instinct and a domesticated confusion within the Cubist-inspired artworks by Tuscan artist, Federico Pinto Schmid. Partially restraining the seemingly boundless color are bold gestures Pinto Schmid creates with swift confidence. Each painting is meant to communicate a multitude of feelings and styles which can be reorganized infinitely within one&#39;s imagination.</p><p>This large one-of-a-kind colorful mixed media painting on canvas measures 48 inches high by 76 inches wide. It is stretched, wired, and ready to hang. It is signed by Pinto on the front and back. Free local Los Angeles area delivery. Affordable Continental U.S. and International shipping available. A certificate of authenticity issued by the gallery is included. This artwork is exhibited at Artplex Gallery, one of the leading international art galleries in Los Angeles.</p><p>Born in Tuscany and raised between Germany and Italy, Pinto Schmid is influenced by particularly German cubism as well as his father’s art practice. Growing up with an ever-present home studio helped push his art practice as he matured. His artworks have been collected and exhibited internationally gracing a number of prominent homes.</p><p>REPRESENTATION<br>Artplex Gallery, Los Angeles</p>', '''Includes gouache; fresco; ink and wash; oil painting; screen painting; scroll painting; tempera; watercolor.''', '''Mixed Media, Acrylic, Oil Pastel on Canvas''', 'https://d7hftxdivxxvm.cloudfront.net?height=800&quality=80&resize_to=fit&src=https%3A%2F%2Fd32dm0rphc51dk.cloudfront.net%2FxnYB812kQd8hlrxB78Oa1w%2Fnormalized.jpg&width=800')    
    INSERT INTO artwork (slug, artwork_name, artist_slug, price, size_in, size_cm, description, additional_information, material, medium, image)    VALUES ('suzanne-vaughan-glowing-evening-diptych-abstract-landscape', 'glowing evening diptych abstract landscape', 'suzanne-vaughan', '140000', '24 × 36 × 1 1/2 in', '61 × 91.4 × 3.8 cm', 'None', '<p>“Glowing Evening” is an original oil painting from my abstract landscape collection. This collection draws inspiration from the natural world ~ the contours of the land and hills, the sky’s atmosphere and cloud formations, the flow of the sea and rivers. These shapes and forms are abstracted to their energetic essence and combined with the vibrant colors that I love so much. Each unique painting has a modern minimal aesthetic in a wide array of energetic color palettes to add some fresh energy and vitality to any space. The sky glows in soft shades of orange, pink and purple as the sun illuminates the clouds while setting in the sky. A thin strip of water is lit up with a reddish glow being framed by distant hills and the shoreline above a rich brown foreground. It captures the magical feeling of twilight, where the light softens and warms at the end of the day. The rich warm colors create a calm and soothing feeling combined with the peaceful tranquility of the water reflections. This painting is a Diptych - Two gallery wrapped canvases 24”H x 18”W x 1.5” - Total size 24”H x 36”W Painted on a 1.5” gallery wrapped canvas with the edges painted white and finished with a coat of protective varnish, it comes ready to hang and signed on the front. Thank you for your interest in my work. Best Suzanne International buyers Please note - Any VAT, Customs Duty or Import fees to be paid by buyer. :: Painting :: Abstract :: This piece comes with an official certificate of authenticity signed by the artist :: Ready to Hang: Yes :: Signed: Yes :: Signature Location: Signed on the Front :: Canvas :: Landscape :: Original :: Framed: No:: Condition: New</p>', '''Includes gouache; fresco; ink and wash; oil painting; screen painting; scroll painting; tempera; watercolor.''', '''Painting, Oil on Canvas''', 'https://d7hftxdivxxvm.cloudfront.net?height=480&quality=80&resize_to=fit&src=https%3A%2F%2Fd32dm0rphc51dk.cloudfront.net%2FMvILXcTVfzkHnHiFYNAaxQ%2Fnormalized.jpg&width=800')    
